item.title: Wait But Why?
item.description: My workplace generously allowed me to take some personal-leave time after a rough & tumble start to 2017. I’ll use the time to go Fully Concentrated on learning to program, something I’ve been exploring very-part-time for about a year. That seems fine. Except, oh wait, why? No one who looked into my humanities-riddled education would likely suggest I take up computer programming as a natural fit. But spending the last few years in tech, Iâ€™ve come to a conclusion about myself:
